{"type":"message","id":"3edd1182","parentId":"f3be0b44","timestamp":"2026-03-09T17:42:08.587Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_01RH1wrCvbn8FCuwq9JnNEBB","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Usage:\n  qmd collection add [path] --name <name> --mask <pattern>  - Create/index collection\n  qmd collection list           - List all collections with details\n  qmd collection remove <name>  - Remove a collection by name\n  qmd collection rename <old> <new>  - Rename a collection\n  qmd ls [collection[/path]]    - List collections or files in a collection\n  qmd context add [path] \"text\" - Add context for path (defaults to current dir)\n  qmd context list              - List all contexts\n  qmd context rm <path>         - Remove context\n  qmd get <file>[:line] [-l N] [--from N]  - Get document (optionally from line, max N lines)\n  qmd multi-get <pattern> [-l N] [--max-bytes N]  - Get multiple docs by glob or comma-separated list\n  qmd status                    - Show index status and collections\n  qmd update [--pull]           - Re-index all collections (--pull: git pull first)\n  qmd embed [-f]                - Create vector embeddings (900 tokens/chunk, 15% overlap)\n  qmd cleanup                   - Remove cache and orphaned data, vacuum DB\n  qmd query <query>             - Search with query expansion + reranking (recommended)\n  qmd search <query>            - Full-text keyword search (BM25, no LLM)\n  qmd vsearch <query>           - Vector similarity search (no reranking)\n  qmd mcp                       - Start MCP server (stdio transport)\n  qmd mcp --http [--port N]     - Start MCP server (HTTP transport, default port 8181)\n  qmd mcp --http --daemon       - Start MCP server as background daemon\n  qmd mcp stop                  - Stop background MCP daemon\n\nGlobal options:\n  --index <name>             - Use custom index name (default: index)\n\nSearch options:\n  -n <num>                   - Number of results (default: 5, or 20 for --files)\n  --all                      - Return all matches (use with --min-score to filter)\n  --min-score <num>          - Minimum similarity score\n  --full                     - Output full document instead of snippet\n  --line-numbers             - Add line numbers to output\n  --files                    - Output docid,score,filepath,context (default: 20 results)\n  --json                     - JSON output with snippets (default: 20 results)\n  --csv                      - CSV output with snippets\n  --md                       - Markdown output\n  --xml                      - XML output\n  -c, --collection <name>    - Filter results to a specific collection\n\nMulti-get options:\n  -l <num>                   - Maximum lines per file\n  --max-bytes <num>          - Skip files larger than N bytes (default: 10240)\n  --json/--csv/--md/--xml/--files - Output format (same as search)\n\nIndex: /Users/aiagnet/.cache/qmd/index.sqlite"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":680,"aggregated":"Usage:\n  qmd collection add [path] --name <name> --mask <pattern>  - Create/index collection\n  qmd collection list           - List all collections with details\n  qmd collection remove <name>  - Remove a collection by name\n  qmd collection rename <old> <new>  - Rename a collection\n  qmd ls [collection[/path]]    - List collections or files in a collection\n  qmd context add [path] \"text\" - Add context for path (defaults to current dir)\n  qmd context list              - List all contexts\n  qmd context rm <path>         - Remove context\n  qmd get <file>[:line] [-l N] [--from N]  - Get document (optionally from line, max N lines)\n  qmd multi-get <pattern> [-l N] [--max-bytes N]  - Get multiple docs by glob or comma-separated list\n  qmd status                    - Show index status and collections\n  qmd update [--pull]           - Re-index all collections (--pull: git pull first)\n  qmd embed [-f]                - Create vector embeddings (900 